{"tid":1004144,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[調查] 大家對畫鞋(改鞋)有幾多興趣","createTime":"2019-02-01T08:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T01:27:10.000Z","uid":231874,"like":16,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe4ee4fc6e1b1797f463fb0b7b42ccd73b46de9","tid":1004144,"uid":231874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 我係做改鞋呢個樣已經做左三年有多(係幫唔同既客改鞋), 咁3年入黎都算個個月都有2~3單生意, PART TIME 黎講算係唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 咁事源其實有好多客仔都想試下自己改鞋, 但係對皮革/ 布料唔認識, 又驚甩色先唔敢自己黎. 咁我就自己就有對鞋會改 (由全白 改 做紅黑 (Marvel Miles Morales&rsquo; Spiderman) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w39BMnQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw39BMnQ.jpg&h=0162a579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyRHGMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyRHGMn.jpg&h=66bae9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁既樣左右, 睇下有幾多個會有興趣想學個過程. <br />\n<br />\n我都知好多人會話:  改鞋咁同假野有咩分別<br />\n咁我都廢事講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用圖黎表示最好 <br />\nStar war 系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EsPmRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EsPmRf.jpg&h=9f3a7d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJk9mRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJk9mRh.jpg&h=03ef90a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMarvel 系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXEumSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXEumSY.jpg&h=dd1bd978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個客自己油白佢之後出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmQJrjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmQJrjG.jpg&h=2e8a70dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxGDZEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxGDZEK.jpg&h=e1bfc88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jg7GXsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJg7GXsx.jpg&h=362a25da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDOV1Ud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDOV1Ud.jpg&h=fb4c8038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKaws 系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrzYZG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrzYZG1.jpg&h=d95fd3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpWP6m1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpWP6m1.jpg&h=cbc061a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpDiZG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpDiZG2.jpg&h=d758fc7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然仲有其他, 但係廢事放得太多. <br />\n<br />\n睇下大家會唔會有興趣, 如果有反應的話, 先再講個過程要如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea0ce5839eb52228dff1b6bd813a19bb7b40a53","tid":1004144,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"597ff81228c80d9bd0cf461d175ca909b41eb19d","tid":1004144,"uid":231874,"like":41,"dislike":5,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"4ea0ce5839eb52228dff1b6bd813a19bb7b40a53","tid":1004144,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"未來三年會做埋右佢<br />\n再未來三年會做埋你老豆"},{"pid":"46ddd98e318f1cccabbce284a2f66b3246a963bc","tid":1004144,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1a5e0a60fa1e1bcf2a096e565caa6872faa3aee","tid":1004144,"uid":62627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"李生開post  比個正評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5e529fd6c10