.jpg&h=fb810d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yxe6pEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxe6pEo.jpg&h=27bdc46c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似對 豆腐車咁 同WESTBROOK , 2個都係個客中意, 但係市面個到無一對岩心水, 咁就去搵我改鞋. <br />\n我唔會叫自己做 Designer , 因為我無由零自己創作. <br />\n<br />\n利伸: 對豆腐車用左3M係前面, 用閃光燈影佢會發光, 好頂癮<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZ7WMWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZ7WMWb.jpg&h=8641b14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為係VIDEO 到CAP出黎, 所以請原諒"},{"pid":"3d662b330544d70d57d76a045cfa68f2f2a4c3e9","tid":1004144,"uid":231874,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7ffdec1697e3cc1278f14eee5bd13356dd8e1d44","tid":1004144,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"睇人定價錢咁主觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出完po人地有興趣比你改鞋 你又唔留聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 我係做改鞋呢個樣已經做左三年有多(係幫唔同既客改鞋), 咁3年入黎都算個個月都有2~3單生意, PART TIME 黎講算係唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 咁事源其實有好多客仔都想試下自己改鞋,<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 但係對皮革/ 布料唔認識, 又驚甩色先唔敢自己黎. 咁我就自己就有對鞋會改</span></span></strong> (由全白 改 做紅黑 (Marvel Miles Morales&rsquo; Spiderman) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁既樣左右, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下有幾多個會有興趣想學個過程.</span></strong> </span>"},{"pid":"6c9e2fcf61ca841f77a570f0f85b941675fc9b8b","tid":1004144,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bea44ace149058a7ede896f5b05eeb9a4f45ac3","tid":1004144,"uid":231874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ffdec1697e3cc1278f14eee5bd13356dd8e1d44","tid":1004144,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"睇人定價錢咁主觀<img s